%h3 Home

%p
  Welcome to our prototype.
  %br/
  This website is used to create accounts for the Infiltration Prototype Flash Game.

%p
  - if user_signed_in?
    Ok #{current_user.name}, now use your email and password to login when you are in the Flash client (link goes here).
  - else
    If you already have an account, you can go to the Flash client and login from there,
    %br/
    if you don't have an account, please
    = link_to 'Sign up', new_user_registration_path

